      Julian invited you to do an interview with him, saying you've already gone
      beyond English.
  - index: 0
    imageObject: {fileID: 0}
    title: 'End: Poor Student '
    content: You're working very hard; We can see your dedication. Hope you can pay
      more attention to your study methods going forward.
